          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-02-04 23:05:13" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to bewitch a person, frequently by use of the evil eye and with evil intent</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to bewitch</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to practice magic on</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>βασκαίνω[a] differs from {L:μαγεύω&lt;SDBG:μαγεύω:000000&gt;} to practice magic ({D:53.96}) in that the former involves the use of so-called black magic, but for a different interpretation of βασκαίνω in {S:04800300100012}, see {D:88.159}.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
